cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper proposes a process model for the development of machine learning applications and discusses quality assurance methodology. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also addresses project organization and maintenance, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.SE (Software Engineering). Additionally, the paper draws from practical experience and scientific literature, indicating that it could also fit into cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper discusses quality assurance, which could place it in cs.CY (Computers and Society).
